Title: Baelz Hakos
GameText: Power - Chaotic Leader: Either draw 1 card or discover 1 Ongoing card. If no card was played this way, 1 ally Hero may draw 1 card.

- Discard the top card of a deck.
- Play the top card of a deck.
- Discover a One-Shot from a deck.

Title: Absolute Chaos
GameText:
Reveal the top card of your deck. Draw it or replace it.
Play the top card of your deck.
Quote: Yolo is my ninja way!                 It's time to put those moves out on display!

Title: Bruh!
GameText:
1 ally Hero may play the top card of their deck.
If no card was played this way, Bae deals 1 target 4 infernal damage.
Quote: "It's an expression that can               be used in so many different scenarios...   bruh is a way of life."

Title: Chaotic Tactics
GameText:
When you would play a card that shares the name of a card in play, you may first destroy the card in play. If you do, Bae deals up to 3 targets 2 infernal damage each.
POWER: Put up to 1 Ongoing card from your trash on top of your deck. Play the top card of your deck.
Quote:
I got the tactics I need          
Patience is just not for me

Title: Dynamic Relationship
GameText:
Bae may deal 1 ally character 2 fixed psychic damage. That character may deal Bae 2 fixed psychic damage.
Each Hero dealt damage this way may discover 1 Ongoing card or discover 1 Item card.
Quote: "Dear IRyS, You have brought so much happiness to me. Thank you for being in a divorce with me. I love you."

Title: Mr. Squeaks
GameText:
When you would play the top card of your deck, reveal it instead. Then, you may discard it. If you discard a card this way, play 1 card. Otherwise, play it.
START PHASE
You may play the top card of your deck.
Quote: "I don't really pay attention to her. I'm just here to make sure she doesn't die."

Title: Play Dice!
GameText:
After a revealed card is replaced in a deck, you may shuffle that deck. After you do, Bae deals 1 target 2 infernal damage.
POWER: Reveal the top card of a deck. Either replace or discard that card.
Quote: For this moment I am truly really me!

Title: Promise of Chaos
GameText:
3 Heroes may reveal the top card of their respective decks. They may replace or bury those cards.
1 Hero target may deal 1 target 3 infernal damage.
Quote: "I would like to ask for new pants, more rng luck, and world chaos! Strictly for Council work purposes."

Title: Revel in Chaos
GameText:
Destroy up to 2 Ongoing cards.
For each Hero Ongoing card destroyed this way, play the top card of your deck.
Quote: "How many cups of coffee do you need before you completely lose touch with reality and become unhinged?"

Title: The Council - Chaos
GameText:
After this card is played, discover 1 Ongoing card.
After a card in an ally Hero's play area is destroyed, that Hero may draw 1 card.
POWER: Discover 1 One-Shot card. Bae deals 1 target 2 infernal damage.

Title: Toxictaro
GameText:
When this card is destroyed, play the top card of 1 ally Hero's deck and Bae regains 2 HP.
After one of your cards is destroyed, Bae may deal 1 target 2 infernal damage and destroy this card.
REACTION: Bae deals the attacker 2 infernal damage. Destroy this card.
Quote: "You are all beaches. You are all mother freaking beaches. I will not have my Mario Kart legacy like this!!"

Title: Wazzzup!
GameText:
Draw 1 card
Discover 1 Ongoing card.
Bae may deal herself 2 fixed psychic damage. If she does, play the top card of your deck.
Quote: "Wazzzup! Good morning. Ohayo... I have coffee. Cawfeee..."

Title: You Wanna Go?
GameText:
After this card is played, select 1 target. Bae deals that target 3 infernal damage.
When this card is destroyed, play the top card of 1 ally Hero's deck and Bae regains 2 HP.
START PHASE
That target deals Bae 3 melee damage. Destroy this card.
Quote: "Lovers' quarrel?"                    "Bae, I mean, waifu killed me with an axe."

Title: Zoomer Rat
GameText:
Discover 1 Limited card. If no card was played this way, play the top card of your deck.
You may discard 1 card. If you do, you may use 1 power.
Quote: "Do you understand that there was a point in human history where cellphones didn't exist? Can that enter your consciousness? ... I can't talk this way to a senpai."
